Package: bewitch
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Recommends: smartmontools
Description: Server monitoring daemon with TUI
 Bewitch is a lightweight server monitoring tool that collects system metrics
 (CPU, memory, disk, network, temperature, power, processes) and stores them
 in DuckDB. It includes a terminal UI for real-time monitoring and historical
 analysis, plus an alerting system with webhook support.
